ith ferocity.  Forge alliances in guilds, join epic raids and world events, and blaze a path to become the most powerful Agent Zenith has ever known. \n\nFeatures:\n- Explore an ever expanding massive open world through flying, climbing, ziplining, and even swimming!\n- Discover a deep combat system that takes both time and practice to master -- shoot, swing, and cast your way to glory.\n- Synthesize powerful items using the spoils of battle and enhance them to become a legendary Agent.\n- Discover the joy of cooking -- learn delicious recipes, gather ingredients, and share them with your friends.\n- Play together -- conquer Zenith\u2019s greatest challenges, including epic boss battles, public events and dungeons.\n\n", "short_description": "Endless adventure awaits in Zenith, an exhilarating open-world VR MMO!\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://skywave.zenithmmo.com/privacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ramen VR", "support_website_url": "https://zenithmmo.happyfox.com/", "website_url": "https://www.zenithmmo.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "961172191044986"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ADVENTURE", "RPG"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "927856617919517"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 32, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "633936461365575"}, {"status": "PUBLIS